stork.feather

Class Emitter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • stork.feather.Bell
      • stork.feather.Emitter<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Future

    public class Emitter<T>
extends Bell
    An asynchronous analogue to an Iterator based on Bells. This can be used, for instance, to implement an asynchronous producer-consumer solution.
